thrilled that you're here today.

00:00:35.100 --> 00:00:38.860
This is a very special
event, and I'm really excited

00:00:38.860 --> 00:00:41.920
about the panel coming up.

00:00:41.920 --> 00:00:46.650
This is part of an event called
Dancing Ireni, Reimaging,

00:00:46.650 --> 00:00:51.300
Reimagining, Alan Lomax's
choreometrics project.

00:00:51.300 --> 00:00:54.210
We're delighted to be
cosponsoring today's symposium

00:00:54.210 --> 00:00:57.410
with the University of
Maryland School of Theater,

00:00:57.410 --> 00:00:59.600
Dance and Performance Studies.

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:02.840
And today's conversation
