00:01:02.840 --> 00:01:06.950
of a very important landmark
three day conference that's coming

00:01:06.950 --> 00:01:08.930
up on choreometrics.

00:01:08.930 --> 00:01:13.960
The remaining two days are going to
be held free of charge to anyone,

00:01:13.960 --> 00:01:17.820
