These numbers get spitted out.

00:50:28.460 --> 00:50:36.780
Well, just that process.

00:50:36.780 --> 00:50:42.950
How you were sort of feeding things
into Alan, what he was getting

00:50:42.950 --> 00:50:47.970
and then the interpretations
that started coming back to you.

00:50:47.970 --> 00:50:52.930
&gt;&gt; Meriam Lobel: We were
all in the same small office

